  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Classified Dossier",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "机密文件",
    "TraditionalChinese": "機密檔案"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "This report records the history of a planetary facility forming part of the <span class=\"name name-exped\">Utopia Project</span>. Several sections are curiously absent.<br><br>DS 2368 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Facility </span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">founded</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">. Plasma deep drill rig operational.</span><br>DS 2384 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Return growth steady at 1%.</span><br>DS 2400 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Overseers querying growth rate.</span><br>DS 2416 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Orbital exp. approved. Station trade booming.</span><br>DS 2432 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[Redacted]</span> <span class=\"name name-stellar\">hazard encountered.</span><br>DS 2448 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[Redacted]</span><br>DS 2464 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Utopia Project launched.</span><br>DS 2464 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Facility </span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">restored</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">. Plasma deep drill rig operational. Trade routes re-opened.</span><br>DS 2480 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[Redacted]</span><br>DS 2496 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Facility </span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">restored</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">. Plasma deep drill rig operational. Trade routes re-opened.</span><br>DS 2512 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[Redacted]</span><br><br>The last two entries are repeated over and over, across hundreds of pages.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这份报告记录了作为<span class=\"name name-exped\">乌托邦项目</span>一部分的一处行星设施的历史。令人好奇的是，记录中缺失了多个部分。<br><br>DS2368 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">设施</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">建立</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">。等离子深层钻井运作正常。</span><br>DS2384 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">回归增长率稳定在1%。</span><br>DS2400 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">监督者们对增长率进行了问询。</span><br>DS2416 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">轨道层扩建已得到批准。空间站贸易如火如荼。</span><br>DS2432 :: 遭遇<span class=\"name name-special\">[已修订]</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">危害</span><br>DS2448 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已修订]</span><br>DS2464 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">启动乌托邦项目。</span><br>DS2464 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">设施</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">修复</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">。等离子深层钻井运作正常。贸易路线重启。</span><br>DS2480 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已修订]</span><br>DS2496 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">设施</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">修复</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">。等离子深层钻井运作正常。贸易路线重启。</span><br>DS2512 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已修订]</span><br><br>接下来长达数百页的内容都在反复重复日志中的最后两行条目。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "此報告記錄著<span class=\"name name-exped\">烏托邦計畫</span>下，一座星球設施的歷史。數個篇章有異常缺失現象。<br><br>DS 2368 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">設施</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">成立</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">。電漿深層鑽探設備可正常運行。</span><br>DS 2384 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">回報成長率穩定維持在 1%。</span><br>DS 2400 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">監督者詢問成長率狀況。</span><br>DS 2416 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">已批准軌道擴張，太空站貿易蓬勃發展。</span><br>DS 2432 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已刪改]</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">遭遇風險。</span><br>DS 2448 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已刪改]</span><br>DS 2464 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">烏托邦計畫啟動。</span><br>DS 2464 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">設施</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已修復</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">。電漿深層鑽探設備可正常運行。貿易路線已重新開啟。</span><br>DS 2480 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已刪改]</span><br>DS 2496 :: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">設施</span><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已修復</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">。電漿深層探鑽設備可正常運行。貿易路線已重新開啟。</span><br>DS 2512 :: <span class=\"name name-special\">[已刪改]</span><br><br>最後兩項紀錄一再重複，佔據了幾百頁的空間。"
  },
